### Set these first
@host = http://localhost:4000
# Paste a Supabase access token (from your web/mobile client after sign-in):
@token = PASTE_SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 1. Complete onboarding (creates the organisation + owner membership)
POST {{host}}/v1/onboarding
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessName": "Ampere Studio",
  "category": "Agency",
  "currency": "RWF",
  "fullName": "Happy Axel"
}

### 2. Confirm you are onboarded
GET {{host}}/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Create and send an invoice in one call
# Customer is created inline. Response includes public_link + whatsapp_share_text.
POST {{host}}/v1/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": { "name": "Acme Ltd", "email": "pay@acme.rw" },
  "amount": 450000,
  "dueDate": "2026-06-30",
  "description": "Website design — phase 1",
  "send": true
}

### 4. List invoices
GET {{host}}/v1/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. The public invoice page (no auth) — paste the token from step 3's public_link
GET {{host}}/v1/public/invoice/PASTE_PUBLIC_TOKEN

### 6. Mark it paid — paste the invoice id from step 3
POST {{host}}/v1/invoices/PASTE_INVOICE_ID/mark-paid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Customer profile with computed balance — paste the customer id
GET {{host}}/v1/customers/PASTE_CUSTOMER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
